  "key_findings": [
    "CBSA provides multiple formats for tariff data access",
    "Microsoft Access database is best for bulk download without authentication",
    "CARM API requires portal registration but offers programmatic access",
    "Canada uses 10-digit HS codes for imports (extends 6-digit international standard)",
    "MFN duty rates are available in all provided formats",
    "No free public API with open documentation found - CARM API documentation requires portal login",
    "Canada Tariff Finder tool is web-based only, no API access",
    "Extended HS codes (10-digit) include Canadian-specific tariff items (digits 7-8) for precise duty determination"
  ],
